snippet.title: Gunslinger: Become The Most Wanted
snippet.description:
Are you the good, the bad or the best?
Take your mobile, get ready and Snap! With Gunslinger you can duel old west style anywhere, and show who is the fastest Gunslinger in town. Become a Gunslinger searching for bounties on the heads of other Gunslingers.
Download here!: https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.softnstuff.gunslinger
